commands.name: az palo-alto cloudngfw local-rulestack fqdnlist create
commands.syntax:
az palo-alto cloudngfw local-rulestack fqdnlist create --fqdn-list
                                                       --local-rulestack-name
                                                       --name
                                                       --resource-group
                                                       [--audit-comment]
                                                       [--description]
                                                       [--etag]
                                                       [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
examples: az palo-alto cloudngfw local-rulestack fqdnlist create -g MyResourceGroup --local-rulestack-name MyLocalRulestacks --name MyFqdnlist --audit-comment "string" --description "description" --fqdn-list "string1" "string2"

commands.name: az palo-alto cloudngfw local-rulestack fqdnlist delete

                                                       [--local-rulestack-name]
                                                       [--name]
                                                       [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                       [--resource-group]
                                                       [--subscription]
examples: az palo-alto cloudngfw local-rulestack fqdnlist delete  -g MyResourceGroup --local-rulestack-name MyLocalRulestacks --name MyFqdnlist
